Enum MarkerType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<MarkerType>
      • com.gembox.spreadsheet.charts.MarkerType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<MarkerType>

    public enum MarkerType
extends Enum<MarkerType>
    Represents a marker symbol which will be used on each LineChartSeries data point.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      AUTO
